---
import { SignedIn, SignedOut, SignInButton } from "@clerk/astro/components";
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Background decorations -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full">
        <div class="absolute top-20 right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-blue-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-20 left-10 w-32 h-32 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-xl opacity-70"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7"></path>
                </svg>
                Proceso simple y rápido
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                ¿Cómo funciona 
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">QR Boxes</span>?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Organiza tu mudanza en 4 pasos simples. Desde crear cajas hasta encontrar tus objetos, 
                todo el proceso está diseñado para ser intuitivo y eficiente.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Steps -->
        <div class="grid gap-12 lg:gap-16">
            <!-- Step 1 -->
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-500 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg mr-4 shadow-lg">
                            1
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-500 flex-1 ml-4"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Crea y registra tus cajas</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Añade cajas a tu dashboard y asígnales nombres descriptivos como "Cocina", "Dormitorio" o "Oficina". 
                        Cada caja obtiene un ID único y un código QR personalizado.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="text-gray-600">Nombres personalizables y categorización por habitaciones</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-100">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6 flex items-center">
                                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path>
                                </svg>
                                Create New Box
                            </h2>
                            <div class="space-y-4">
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Box Name *</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-blue-50" placeholder="Cocina - Utensilios" disabled />
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Room</label>
                                    <input type="text" class="w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-lg bg-blue-50" placeholder="Cocina" disabled />
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-2">Items in this box</label>
                                    <div class="space-y-2 mb-3">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                                            <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Platos</span>
                                            <button class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 text-xs">×</button>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-2 bg-gray-100 rounded-lg">
                                            <span class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Cubiertos</span>
                                            <button class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 text-xs">×</button>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-500 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg">
                                        Create QR Box
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-green-500 text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 2 -->
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl max-w-md w-full p-6 border border-gray-100">
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">QR Code</h3>
                                <button class="text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700">
                                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-center space-y-4">
                                <div class="mb-2 font-semibold">Cocina - Utensilios</div>
                                <div class="bg-white p-3 inline-block rounded-lg shadow-sm border-2 border-gray-100 mb-3">
                                    <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-white border border-gray-300 relative">
                                        <!-- QR Code más realista -->
                                        
                                        <!-- Cuadrado de posicionamiento superior izquierdo -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-6 h-6 bg-black">
                                            <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-4 h-4 bg-white">
                                                <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Cuadrado de posicionamiento superior derecho -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-1 right-1 w-6 h-6 bg-black">
                                            <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-4 h-4 bg-white">
                                                <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Cuadrado de posicionamiento inferior izquierdo -->
                                        <div class="absolute bottom-1 left-1 w-6 h-6 bg-black">
                                            <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-4 h-4 bg-white">
                                                <div class="absolute top-1 left-1 w-2 h-2 bg-black"></div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Líneas de timing horizontales -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-6 left-8 right-8 h-px bg-black"></div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Líneas de timing verticales -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-8 bottom-8 left-6 w-px bg-black"></div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Patrón de datos en el centro -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-8 left-8 right-8 bottom-8 grid grid-cols-4 gap-0">
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-white m-px"></div>
                                            <div class="bg-black m-px"></div>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <!-- Puntos adicionales para simular datos -->
                                        <div class="absolute top-2 left-8 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute top-3 left-9 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute top-4 left-8 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute top-2 right-8 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute top-3 right-9 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute bottom-2 left-8 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                        <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-9 w-1 h-1 bg-black"></div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">Scan this QR code to access box content</div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-end mt-6 gap-2">
                                <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                                    Download QR
                                </button>
                                <button class="bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg">
                                    Close
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-green-500 text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg animate-pulse">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3M3 17V7a2 2 0 012-2h6l2 2h6a2 2 0 012 2v10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg mr-4 shadow-lg">
                            2
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-blue-500 flex-1 ml-4"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Descarga e imprime los QRs</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Genera códigos QR únicos para cada caja y descárgalos en alta resolución. 
                        Imprime las etiquetas y pégalas en tus cajas para identificarlas fácilmente.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-gray-600">Descarga en formato PDF o PNG</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-gray-600">Calidad de impresión optimizada</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 -->
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg mr-4 shadow-lg">
                            3
                        </div>
                        <div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex-1 ml-4"></div>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Registra el contenido</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        Añade los objetos que vas guardando en cada caja. Describe cada artículo y 
                        organízalos por categorías para encontrarlos más fácilmente después.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-3">
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-gray-600">Descripciones detalladas de cada objeto</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                            <span class="text-gray-600">Categorización automática por habitación</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-100">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 flex items-center">
                                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-600 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h8a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    Items in this box
                                </h3>
                            </div>
                            
                            <!-- Items List Container -->
                            <div class="space-y-2">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors group">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">1</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Platos (8 unidades)</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 hover:bg-red-50 p-2 rounded-lg transition-all">
                                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors group">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">2</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Cubiertos de plata</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 hover:bg-red-50 p-2 rounded-lg transition-all">
                                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors group">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">3</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Tazas de café (6)</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <button class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-800 hover:bg-red-50 p-2 rounded-lg transition-all">
                                        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 7l-.867 12.142A2 2 0 0116.138 21H7.862a2 2 0 01-1.995-1.858L5 7m5 4v6m4-6v6m1-10V4a1 1 0 00-1-1h-4a1 1 0 00-1 1v3M4 7h16"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-purple-500 text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 4 -->
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <div class="relative">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-6 border border-gray-100">
                            <!-- Header -->
                            <div class="text-center mb-6">
                                <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
                                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center h-16 w-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-blue-400 text-white rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                                        <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20 7l-8-4-8 4m16 0l-8 4m8-4v10l-8 4m0-10L4 7m8 4v10M4 7v10l8 4"></path>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Cocina - Utensilios</h1>
                                <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full mb-2">
                                    <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                                    </svg>
                                    Cocina
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">Box Contents</p>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Box Content -->
                            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-green-50 p-4 border-b rounded-t-lg">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                                    <div class="flex-1">
                                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                                            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Cocina - Utensilios</h2>
                                        </div>
                                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1">
                                            Created: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="text-right ml-4">
                                        <div class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-sm font-medium px-3 py-1 rounded-full">
                                            3 items
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Items List -->
                            <div class="p-4 space-y-2">
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">1</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Platos (8 unidades)</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">2</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Cubiertos de plata</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-8 h-8 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-full mr-3 text-sm font-medium">3</div>
                                        <span class="text-gray-900">Tazas de café (6)</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-indigo-500 text-white p-3 rounded-full shadow-lg">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 21l-6-6m2-5a7 7 0 11-14 0 7 7 0 0114 0z"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-500 text-white rounded-xl font-bold text-lg mr-4 shadow-lg">
                            4
                        </div>
